co-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xou1665702811617.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xou1665702811617.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xou1665702811617.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xou1665702811617\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                \n Edit Triggers: Menu\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use the Trigger Editor to define menu-level triggers.\n </p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xou1665702811617__li_d3470e1_d3471e1_d3472e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ckm1665702665911.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ckm1665702665911.html\" title=\"System trigger that is executed before a menu or menu item is displayed.\">trigger preDisplay</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xou1665702811617__li_d3473e1_d3474e1_d3475e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"prp1665702665837.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/prp1665702665837.html\" title=\"Determines whether the new implementation should use the description and comments defined in the component's specification.\">Option: Copy Description and Comments</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xou1665702811617__section_lp4_dbg_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d453321e74\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Use the Trigger Editor to navigate and edit ProcScript in the triggers of menus and\n            panels. </p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xou1665702811617__ul_i1k_fbg_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xou1665702811617__li_d3476e1_d3477e1_d3478e1\">To start the Trigger Editor, click\n                  <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Triggers</span> in the Menu or Panel Library editor. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xou1665702811617__li_d3479e1_d3480e1_d3481e1\">To navigate or select other menus, return to the\n               Menu editor. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xou1665702811617__li_d3482e1_d3483e1_d3484e1\">To tag triggers that you want to find easily, select\n               the trigger and click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Mark</span>. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xou1665702811617__section_dmp_fbg_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d453321e101\">Panes</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xou1665702811617__p_d6998e1_d6999e1_d7000e1\">The Trigger Editor consists of the following resizable\n            panes:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xou1665702811617__ul_fpq_gbg_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xou1665702811617__li_d3485e1_d3486e1_d3487e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xou1665702811617__p_d7001e1_d7002e1_d7003e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mnq1665702811829.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mnq1665702811829.html\" title=\"The Structure pane displays the hierarchical structure of the menu. Use it to navigate to the menu object you want to edit.\">Structure</a>—view and navigate\n                  the hierarchical structure of the current menu</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xou1665702811617__li_d3488e1_d3489e1_d3490e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xou1665702811617__p_d7004e1_d7005e1_d7006e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jpi1665702811897.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jpi1665702811897.html\" title=\"The Triggers pane lists the triggers available for the menu item selected in the Structure pane. Use the Triggers pane to select the trigger you want to edit.\">Triggers</a>—view and navigate\n                  the triggers available to the current object. The icon beside each trigger\n                  indicates whether the trigger contains content or is inherited.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xou1665702811617__li_d3491e1_d3492e1_d3493e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xou1665702811617__p_d7007e1_d7008e1_d7009e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fid1665702811966.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fid1665702811966.html\" title=\"The Trigger editor for Menus enables you to edit the ProcScript for drop-down menus and menu items. It features syntax highlighting, syntax checking, keyword completion, and context-sensitive help for ProcScript keywords.\">Trigger Editor for Menus</a>—view and edit\n                  ProcScript in the current trigger.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xou1665702811617__li_d3494e1_d3495e1_d3496e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xou1665702811617__p_d7010e1_d7011e1_d7012e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kuk1665702812056.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kuk1665702812056.html\" title=\"Tags are shortcuts to ProcScript modules. The Tags pane lists the tags available in the current trigger.\">Tags</a>—view and navigate\n                  to tagged triggers that match search criteria (when you use\n                     <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Find</span>) or contain errors (after a syntax check).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xou1665702811617__section_kkw_hbg_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d453321e164\">Toolbar</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xou1665702811617__p_d7016e1_d7017e1_d7018e1\">Items in the toolbar are also available in the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit</span>, and\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">View</span> menus.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"xou1665702811617__table_d596e1_d597e1_d598e1_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"xou1665702811617__table_d596e1_d597e1_d598e1_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"xou1665702811617__table_d596e1_d597e1_d598e1\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdo